{"tid":387712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［食女系列］有外遇搬走 凌晨攜刀返家行兇狠夫掟妻落街再跳樓亡","createTime":"2017-09-05T00:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T07:36:53.000Z","uid":6181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e983eef541027296bb24dbb18e743e6e43bacbe0","tid":387712,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"有外遇搬走　凌晨攜刀返家行兇狠夫掟妻落街再跳樓亡<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170905&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20143235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170905%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20143235&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1796f9f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170905%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20143235&h=7512ba08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170905&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20143235</a><br />\n<br />\n據警方向兩名死者家屬了解得知，方較早前向親友透露懷疑丈夫有外遇，並曾偷看丈夫手機，更有傳她打算請私家偵探去跟蹤丈夫，最近，方更向家人透露欲與丈夫離婚。至於被揭發有外遇的周偉輝，據悉是在Instagram認識了一名女大學生，並與對方發生了婚外情。<br />\n警方消息稱，案中夫妻上周五在家中因感情問題爭吵，周當晚搬離住所，雙方家人稍後均得知此事，而周離家後住進九龍城沙浦道一家酒店。<br />\n直至昨凌晨4時24分，周偉輝在九龍城沙浦道截乘一部的士，前往御金．國峯住所，懷疑兩人又發生激烈爭執，有人情緒失控，用一把6吋長陶瓷刀猛刺妻子，其後懷疑將傷重倒地的妻子，從28樓住所掟落街，之後跳樓自殺同死。<br />\n<br />\n條仔咁柒 點解都食到咁多女嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b603c355139e1bcd8d7717d3499e8f263a3696a","tid":387712,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"朋友眼中模範夫妻<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170905&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20143252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170905%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20143252&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a3b860ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170905%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20143252&h=67857711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170905&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20143252</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116abf2b13d5a547ca49889676a0f981dd7b2c3f","tid":387712,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔知個女大學生會唔會有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40efefa28a35e0533c4c3b065f090dac307f48c","tid":387712,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"一定係離婚，女方要分曬條仔d身家，所以動殺機<br />\n<br />\n利申：神探"},{"pid":"d0f5e82e27e557ff5455030033dc4620fb6e292e","tid":387712,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勞</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0348c509bc1a2f8fe6a246095415b3643f56190","tid":387712,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5054e550e1859a73fabc52c689a4179836f63f46","tid":387712,"uid":21279,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定係離婚，女方要分曬條仔d身家，所以動殺機<br />\n<br />\n利申：神探</blockquote><br />\n打平均再分嫁<br />\n點睇都係條仔分條女身家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9937d94ddeceff27c44e7e3ade2375c10315adb5","tid":387712,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b67180897fe4f0891cf13ba7f3b9a62ea6f4395","tid":387712,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定係離婚，女方要分曬條仔d身家，所以動殺機<br />\n<br />\n利申：神探</blockquote><br />\n打平均再分嫁<br />\n點睇都係條仔分條女身家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"